gory:Uzbekistan Cup|2016]]\n", "text_old": "{{infobox football tournament season\n|title= O'zbekiston Kubogi 2016\n|year=\n|other_title= \n|image=\n|imagesize=\n|caption=\n|country={{UZB}}\n|num_teams=\n|champions= [[Lokomotiv Tashkent]]\n|runner-up= [[Nasaf Qarshi]]\n|matches= \n|goals=\n|top goal scorer=\n|player=\n|prevseason=[[2015 Uzbekistan Cup|2015]]\n|nextseason=[[2017 Uzbekistan Cup|2017]]\n}}\nThe '''2016 Uzbekistan Cup''' is the 24th season of the annual [[Uzbekistan Cup|Uzbek football Cup]] competition.  The competition started on 14 March 2016 and ended in November 2016.\nThe cup winner is guaranteed a place in the [[2017 AFC Champions League]].\n\n==Matches==\n=== First Round ===\n{{football box collapsible\n|round      = \n|date       = 14 March 2016\n|time       = \n|team1      = [[Pakhtakor-2]] \n|score      = 1\u20130\n|aet        = \n|report     = \n|team2      = '''Lokomotiv BFK Tashkent \n|goals1     = \n|goals2     = \n|stadium    = \n|location   = \n|attendance = \n|referee    = \n|stack      = Y\n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|round      = \n|date       = 14 March 2016\n|time       = \n|team1      = [[FK Orol Nukus]] \n|score      = 2\u20131\n|aet        = \n|report     = \n|team2      = '''[[Xorazm FK Urganch]] \n|goals1     = \n|goals2     = \n|stadium    = \n|location   = \n|attendance = \n|referee    = \n|stack      = Y\n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|round      = \n|date       = 14 March 2016\n|time       = \n|team1      = Nurafshon Bukhara \n|score      = 2\u20131\n|aet        = \n|report     = \n|team2      = '''FK Gijduvan \n|goals1     = \n|goals2     = \n|stadium    = \n|location   = \n|attendance = \n|referee    = \n|stack      = Y\n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|round      = \n|date       = 14 March 2016\n|time       = \n|team1      = '''[[Nasaf-2]] \n|score      = 1\u20131\n|aet          = yes\n|penaltyscore = 1\u20133\n|report     = \n|team2      = [[Mash\u02bcal-2]] \n|goals1     = \n|goals2     = \n|stadium    = \n|locat